 IMPORTANT: Starting From 2001/04/15, The DB2LaTeX XSL stylesheets project
is hosted at SourceForge. Please update your bookmarks.  The URL for the project is
http://db2latex.sourceforge.net and the associated sourceforge entry can be found in
http://www.sourceforge.net/projects/db2latex. I have set up two mailing lists and a
CVS repository. See the SourceForge documentation for details, and do not hesitate to
contact me for further information.  Ramon Casellas, DB2LaTeX mantainer 



